          <li><strong>Economics</strong><br><span class="xpander">The Bachelor of Arts in economics offers in-depth knowledge of how markets work and an understanding of how government intervention affects the economy. Mathematics and statistics serve as analytical tools for undergraduate studies. Students delve into specialized areas, including: 
            <ul class="tight"> 
