          <li><strong>Sociology</strong><br><span class="xpander">Students who earn a Bachelor of Arts or Bachelor of Science participate in an expansive and challenging curriculum, focused on understanding the social universe. Students will receive individual attention from the faculty in a broad range of topics, including: 
